title: catch up with the gals: brooke’s 25th birthday, coachella thoughts + more
itunes:title: catch up with the gals: brooke’s 25th birthday, coachella thoughts + more
description:
Brooke and Danielle are debreifing on Brooke’s big 25th birthday weekend!  The gals talk about Brooke’s party, what else they got into this weekend, and of course - the coachella of it all.  Tune in to hear their thoughts on the festival this year, and so much more! Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
